From the wastelands a figure raced to the base. It had been some time since 
she had been with her companions & fellow warriors. The time in the wilderness 
had given her... new insight. T'was amazing... a pity the Autobots or even 
their decendents may never truly understand the laws of the wild. 

Bounding to the side overlooking the base. Her clear eyes flashed red. Then 
she made her way to the base. 

"Decepticon Base! Respond! This is Maxima. Requesting clearance to enter!" As 
she made her way to the base.
